<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Elearning Activation Email</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body{
            margin:0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #FAFAFA;
            color: #222222;
        }
        a{
            color:#000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        h1{
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p{
            margin: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        table td{
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .email-wrapper{
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .emal-header{
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color:#ffffff;
        }
        .email-body{
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .eamil-footer{
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size:16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="emal-header">   
            <h1>Welcome to Elerning</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <%= user.name %></p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with elearning. To activate your account, please use the follwing activation code :</p>
            <h2><%= activationCode%></h2>
            <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minites.</p>
            <p>If you did not register for a Elearning account,please ingore this email</p>
        </div>
        <div class="eamil-footer">  
            <p>If you have any question, plaese don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:parthdesai132@gmail.com"> support@becodemy.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>